summary.para: Defines the Context Class.
This class is available in Office 2007 and above.
When the object is serialized out as xml, it's qualified name is inkml:context.

Docs.remarks:
The following table lists the possible child types:
Canvas <inkml:canvas>
CanvasTransform <inkml:canvasTransform>
TraceFormat <inkml:traceFormat>
InkSource <inkml:inkSource>
Brush <inkml:brush>
Timestamp <inkml:timestamp>
